Title: For invalid instructions the API should give a 400 response
WHen initial position is out of range the API should give 400 response
When we send a room with negative dimensions the API should give 400 response
If patches are out of range the API should return 400 response
When we send more than two dimensional room API should return an error code
When we send more than two dimensional initial position API should return an error code
When we send more than two dimensional dirt patches API should return an error code
When we send no room dimensions API should return 500 error code
